                    </div>
                    <span>Set and manage your expectations with Barry Moltz's book.  
<br />
<br />If you have not started your business, just started out, or need a new approach to energize a struggling business, read "You Need To Be A Little Crazy".
<br />
<br />Barry shares his insights and experiences to help entrepreneurs navigate the crazy, perilous, rewarding journey of starting a small business.
<br />
<br />This book resonated with me at my core.  While confirming my "craziness" as a serial entrepreneur, Barry's work also reaffirmed and strengthened my driving passions.
<br />
<br />I plan to share many passages from this book with friends and family in the hopes that Barry's words will help them better understand who I am and why I do what I do.
<br />
<br />Thanks Barry!</span>
                  
              
